*Sjajan* dan obasjava beogradske ulice. (A brilliant day is illuminating the streets of Belgrade.)

Pravi *sjajan* poklon za nju bi bila knjiga. (A real brilliant gift for her would be a book.)

On je divan i *sjajan* čovek. (He is a wonderful and brilliant man.)

Ona je imala *sjajan* plan, ali nije uspela da ga sprovede u delo. (She had a brilliant plan, but she failed to put it into action.)

Uložio je mnogo truda u svoj *sjajan* rad. (He put a lot of effort into his brilliant work.)